{"tid":1898851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致各個香港人，要贏就要惡撚過敵人","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T12:13:16.000Z","uid":31181,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7af58018755e3fe99f2e8bb2c08e098df90320","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"首先好感激醫護率先破窗，透過罷工迫政府封關，<br />\n你哋之前所做嘅所有決定，完全正確。<br />\n<br />\n依家面臨一個問題就係秋後算帳，呢個問題唔係因為你哋罷工而成，而係香港人團結反抗的契機。只要大家同心協力，就好大機會成功。<br />\n<br />\n俾個例子，印度呢啲所謂&rdquo;濕鳩&rdquo;國家其實多次侵犯支那邊境，但係支那粒聲唔出，因為印度人夠惡。俄羅斯凶咗兩凶滿清政府，無啦啦就得到左海參崴，因為夠惡。<br />\n<br />\n請大家停止屌醫護去得唔夠盡，槍打出頭鳥，點都會受傷。我哋更加應該並肩而行，齊上齊落。"},{"pid":"1ad32335e2b433be98b3c87bcd97c8790e2a462a","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75e475057477dae6dd8489bf58c96284cb7096a9","tid":1898851,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"搞無差別吧啦"},{"pid":"8c4376a28364db64ad9a732c25a7ab87a14aff3f","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3a682f21ab60fbd3362c333c05ff170c950957","tid":1898851,"uid":292710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab7af58018755e3fe99f2e8bb2c08e098df90320","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"首先好感激醫護率先破窗，透過罷工迫政府封關，<br />\n你哋之前所做嘅所有決定，完全正確。<br />\n<br />\n依家面臨一個問題就係秋後算帳，呢個問題唔係因為你哋罷工而成，而係香港人團結反抗的契機。只要大家同心協力，就好大機會成功。<br />\n<br />\n俾個例子，印度呢啲所謂&rdquo;濕鳩&rdquo;國家其實多次侵犯支那邊境，但係支那粒聲唔出，因為印度人夠惡。俄羅斯凶咗兩凶滿清政府，無啦啦就得到左海參崴，因為夠惡。<br />\n<br />\n請大家停止屌醫護去得唔夠盡，槍打出頭鳥，點都會受傷。我哋更加應該並肩而行，齊上齊落。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"財政預算修正案：<br />\n1. 取消代繳HKDSE，鼓勵學生去英美名校留學。<br />\n2. 取消HKDSE制度，鼓勵公立教育國際化(SAT/IB/GCE)。<br />\n3. 保障市場有2億個口罩供應(一個月存量)。<br />\n4. 鼓勵公立大學私有化，鼓勵學術自由，避免政治干涉學術。<br />\n5. 標準工時"},{"pid":"6da99e2b08b605c605d33848a2a75f04dd860196","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f95f72c9aac9ad4d1ff538066a762c6937923787","tid":1898851,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"左膠+傻鳩黃屍: 嘩你惡過共慘黨，唔好睇呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beb94d7f184f84b236fb3aa7f07f742ddc6f459","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f95f72c9aac9ad4d1ff538066a762c6937923787","tid":1898851,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"左膠+傻鳩黃屍: 嘩你惡過共慘黨，唔好睇呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"阻膠唔係同路人<br />\n係黃都會支持手足所有行動"},{"pid":"e3a53b08891aedcc0066d28f6ce35a7897a776a4","tid":1898851,"uid":343239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"同香港人講要惡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0a71975e9e11842121933fc8624aa4ec91bbb0","tid":1898851,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a53b08891aedcc0066d28f6ce35a7897a776a4","tid":1898851,"uid":343239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"同香港人講要惡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"唔試點知唔得"},{"pid":"b8f0912cb2168e82b4b917b55628bc7154a49cf8","tid":1898851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳】「寧願最後徒勞無功 也不選擇無動於衷」去面對立法會選舉！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\